$ %ProgramFiles%\WindowsPowerShell\Modules

{ Modules

  `%ProgramFiles%\Documents\WindowsPowerShell\Modules` is the default location for → Windows/PowerShell/language/module[PowerShell modules] that are
  → Windows/PowerShell/command-inventory/noun/module/install[installed] for the *current user*.

}
{ Profiles

  This directory might also store one or both of the profile files
    • `Microsoft.PowerShell_profile.ps1`
    • `profile.ps1`

  See also the → Windows/PowerShell/language/variable/automatic/profile[automatic variable `$profile`]

}
